  "extract": "Nobara Linux is a Linux distribution based on Fedora Linux. It is developed by Thomas Crider, otherwise more colloquially referred to as \"Glorious Eggroll\", who is also known for developing Proton-GE, a modification of Valve Corporation's compatibility layer, widely used for running Windows games on Linux.",
  "extract_html": "<p><b>Nobara Linux</b> is a Linux distribution based on Fedora Linux. It is developed by Thomas Crider, otherwise more colloquially referred to as \"Glorious Eggroll\", who is also known for developing Proton-GE, a modification of Valve Corporation's compatibility layer, widely used for running Windows games on Linux.</p>"
